stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE: Reset

    IDLE --> WAIT_DESC: Software kick
    WAIT_DESC --> PARSE_DESC: Descriptor fetched
    PARSE_DESC --> XFER_DATA: Valid descriptor

    XFER_DATA --> CHECK_NEXT: Transfer complete
    CHECK_NEXT --> WAIT_DESC: More descriptors
    CHECK_NEXT --> COMPLETE: Chain done

    COMPLETE --> IDLE: Interrupt sent

    XFER_DATA --> ERROR: AXI error
    ERROR --> IDLE: Error cleared
